<div class="frame-light">
  <div class="container content">
    <h1>Prizes</h1>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="banner-header">Grand Prize Tracks</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center">There will be one grand prize winning hack for each track.</br>The team that best addresses the issues of that respective track will be awarded <strong>$500</strong> to a track-related non-profit of their choice.</p>
      <% @prizes.each do |p| %>
      <% if p.api == false %>
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <h3 class="text-center"><%= p.title %></h3>
        <div><%= p.html_content.html_safe %></div>
        <% if p.sponsor != nil %>
        <p class="text-center"><strong>Sponsored by</strong></p>
        <a href="<%= p.sponsor.link_url %>"><img class="image-center partner-img" src="sponsors/<%= p.sponsor.image_url %>"></a>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="banner-header">Novice Prize Track</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="container-small">There will be a prize for those who are new to programming or attending a hackathon for the first time. The team or individual that creates the best hack that addresses any of the tracks of impact above <strong>and</strong>  meet the requirements for being a novice will be awarded <strong>$250</strong> to donate to a non-profit of their choice. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="banner-header">Company Sponsored Prizes</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="container-small">
        <li> Esri: <strong>$500</strong> for Best Use of Esri API/SDK Prize</li>
        <li> SQLSentry <strong>$800</strong> to Duke Children’s Hospital for best project on social impact in the children’s community</li>
        <li> Best use of Plaid API - 100x prize, 100 of anything (<strong>$500</strong> max)</li>
        <li> Beginner Prize: <strong>$100</strong> for each team member on programming resources (3) </li>
        <li> Google: Best use of Google APIs/Products: 5 of the new Chromecasts either to top team or top teams until we run out</li>
        <li> Capital One: Best Use of Capital One’s Nessie API. <strong>$100</strong> Amazon gift card for each team member and <strong>$400</strong> to the charity of the team’s choice</li>
        <li>IBM: Best use of Bluemix API</li>
        <li>Yik Yak: Best Location Based App</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <% if @prizes == nil %>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="banner-header">Company Sponsored Prizes</h2>
      </div>
      <% @prizes.each do |p| %>
      <% if p.api == true %>
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <a href="<%= p.sponsor.link_url %>">
          <img class="sponsor-img-small image-center" src="sponsors/<%= p.sponsor.image_url %>">
        </a>
        <h3 class="text-center"><%= p.title %></h3>
        <div><%= p.html_content.html_safe %></div>
      </div>
      <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
